name: 珍妮弗·莫里亚蒂
name_full: 珍妮弗·莫里亚蒂 Jennifer Moriarty
introduction: Jennifer has starred in national commercials (Chobani), music videos ("Living the Dream" by Five Finger Death Punch), and most recently was honored with "Best Actress - Feature Film" at the Houston Horror Film Festival (2021) for her performance as Aunt Tilda in "Bloomfield." With a Masters Degree from Emerson College and a long history of classic and contemporary theatre roles, her streak of film projects will come as no surprise to her friends and colleagues, with two more projects shooting in Fall and Winter 2021.
